Review: We really are all capable of unspeakable evil, aren’t we?
There are many lines in this film that will haunt me for the rest of my life.
Please dear god don’t get my hopes up like that.
“Take your sandals from your feet, for the place on which you are standing is holy ground.”
This movie wants so desperately to be profound, but it unfortunately falls flat on its face.
This might be the most fucked up movie I’ve ever seen
Just… let me… redeem, the mileage!
